u/miff34/eng/archives/?year=1985|archivedate=16 March 2013}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Hugo Carvana]]\n* [[Renata Sorrah]]\n* [[Milton Rodrigues]]\n* Macsuara Kadiweu\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Dumont]]\n* [[Cl\u00e1udio Mamberti]]\n* [[S\u00e9rgio Mamberti]]\n* [[Cl\u00e1udio Marzo]]\n* [[Nina de P\u00e1dua]]\n* [[Jonas Bloch]]\n* [[Chico Diaz]]\n* [[Marcos Palmeira]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|0088756|Avaete, Seed of Revenge}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Avaete Seed Of Revenge}}\n[[Category:1985 films]]\n[[Category:1985 drama films]]\n[[Category:Brazilian films]]\n[[Category:Brazilian drama films]]\n[[Category:Drama films based on actual events]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Bras\u00edlia]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Mato Grosso]]\n[[Category:Films shot in S\u00e3o Paulo]]\n[[Category:Portuguese-language films]]\n[[Category:Best Picture APCA Award winners]]\n\n{{Brazil-film-stub}}\n{{1980s-drama-film-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|1985 film}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2015}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name           = Avaete, Seed of Revenge\n| image          = Avaete, Seed of Revenge.jpg\n| caption        = Film poster\n| director       = [[Zelito Viana]]\n| producer       = Zelito Viana\n| writer         = [[Jos\u00e9 Joffily]]<br>Zelito Viana\n| starring       = [[Hugo Carvana]]<br>[[Renata Sorrah]]\n| music          = [[Egberto Gismonti]]\n| cinematography = Edgar Moura\n| editing        = Gilberto Santeiro\n| studio         = Mapa Filmes<br>[[Embrafilme]]\n| distributor    = Embrafilme\n| released       = {{Film date|df=yes|1985|7||[[Moscow International Film Festival|MIFF]]|ref1=<ref name=\"Moscow1985\"/>|1985|8|26|ref2=<ref name=cinemateca>{{cite web | url=http://cinemateca.gov.br/cgi-bin/wxis.exe/iah/?IsisScript=iah/iah.xis&base=FILMOGRAFIA&lang=p&nextAction=lnk&exprSearch=ID=023152&format=detailed.pft#1 | title=Avaet\u00e9: Semente da Vingan\u00e7a | publisher=[[Cinemateca Brasileira]] | accessdate=22 June 2014 | language=Portuguese}}</ref>}}\n| runtime        = 110 minutes\n| country        = Brazil\n| language       = Portuguese\n}}\n\n'''''Avaete, Seed of Revenge''''' ({{lang-pt|'''Avaet\u00e9: Semente da Vingan\u00e7a'''}}) is a 1985 Brazilian [[drama film]] directed by [[Zelito Viana]]. Based on the massacre of [[Cinta Larga people]] in the region of Fontanillas (now [[Ju\u00edna]], Mato Grosso), it was shot along the [[Juruena River]], [[Mato Grosso]], as well as on locations in [[S\u00e3o Paulo]] and [[Bras\u00edlia]].<ref name=cinemateca/> It was entered into the [[14th Moscow International Film Festival]] where it won the Silver Prize.<ref name=\"Moscow1985\">{{cite web |url=http://www.moscowfilmfestival.ru/miff34/eng/archives/?year=1985 |title=14th Moscow International Film Festival (1985) |accessdate=17 February 2013|work=MIFF|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130316084353/http://moscowfilmfestival.ru/miff34/eng/archives/?year=1985|archivedate=16 March 2013}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n* [[Hugo Carvana]]\n* [[Renata Sorrah]]\n* [[Milton Rodrigues]]\n* Macsuara Kadiweu\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Dumont]]\n* [[Cl\u00e1udio Mamberti]]\n* [[S\u00e9rgio Mamberti]]\n* [[Cl\u00e1udio Marzo]]\n* [[Nina de P\u00e1dua]]\n* [[Jonas Bloch]]\n* [[Chico Diaz]]\n* [[Marcos Palmeira]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|0088756|Avaete, Seed of Revenge}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Avaete Seed Of Revenge}}\n[[Category:1985 films]]\n[[Category:1985 drama films]]\n[[Category:Brazilian films]]\n[[Category:Brazilian drama films]]\n[[Category:Drama films based on actual events]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Bras\u00edlia]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Mato Grosso]]\n[[Category:Films shot in S\u00e3o Paulo]]\n[[Category:Portuguese-language films]]\n[[Category:Best Picture APCA Award winners]]\n\n{{Brazil-film-stub}}\n{{1980s-drama-film-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Lugnuts", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Avaete,_Seed_of_Revenge"}
